docstring.long_description:
Inputs
------
v : Vector
    The input vector to delete from
docstring.short_description: The VECTOR_DELETE node returns a new Vector with elements deleted from requested indices

parameters.name: indices
parameters.description: specified indices to delete value(s) at from the input vector

parameters.name: length
parameters.description: number of elements to delete from the input vector, default is 1 (this only applies when one index is specified for indices parameter)

returns.description: The new vector with element(s) deleted from the input vector
